data.description: Welcome to your spacious retreat in a secure gated community minutes from downtown Oviedo. This delightful 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home boasts an inviting living/dining combination and kitchen with breakfast bar. The area off the kitchen provides a functional workspace that could easily double as a cozy spot for a casual dining table. The bedrooms, including the master suite, are discreetly situated upstairs, ensuring tranquility and privacy. Tucked away neatly, the laundry closet is conveniently positioned among the sleeping quarters. The master bath features a garden tub, perfect for unwinding after a long day. With the added convenience of a separate shower and dual vanities. Outside, a sense of seclusion prevails as the townhome enjoys the advantage of no rear neighbors, providing a private and peaceful outdoor setting. Within the confines of the gated community, a communal pool beckons. Exterior maintenance and lawn care are included. Exterior of home has just been repainted.    Oviedo Park is located close to downtown Oviedo, UCF, Seminole State College & major highways. Easy access to airport. It's also home to top-rated Seminole County public schools. Schedule a showing today!!
